                                 README
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TLM 2.0 introduces a new port style called a "socket", which is a port and an
export combined into one. It is a bidirectional connection between the
initiator and target.

      .---------------.                         .------------.
      |   Initiator   |Socket ----------> Socket|   Target   |
      '---------------'                         '------------'

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

